These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, peas, carrot, eggplant
1. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | cherry | peas | carrot | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola | lemonade | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, singing, reading
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | singing | gardening | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, drama, adventure
1. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | martial-arts | adventure | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, rowing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | badminton | rowing | sailing | cricket |

