.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, lemon, zucchini, cabbage
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the person eating orange and the person eating cabbage##2
3. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
4. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | cabbage | lemon | orange | zucchini |

