.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, electronic, house, dubstep
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | house | electronic | folk | dubstep |

 